ges and Guinness Gravy","publishedAt":"2018-03-09T00:00:00Z","nutrition":{"protein":"16 g","fat":"26 g","uom":"per 1 portion","carbohydrates":"32 g","calories":"1774 kJ \/ 424 kcal"},"usefulItems":"large cast iron skillet","hintsAndTricks":["Serves 6 portions as a side dish or 4 portions as an entrée.","Replace lacinato kale with curly kale."],"basicInfo":["easy","15m","1h 5m","6 portions"]}